posed adiabatically\nto tidal fields of arbitrary magnitudes. We provide an open-source\nimplementation of our model and suggest that it can be used to improve\npredictions of dark matter annihilation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Jul 2022 18:00:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2023 11:00:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
