llel to the longer axis of the perturbed\ndisk. Numerical investigations on the full Schnakenberg PDE are performed for\nvarious domains $\\Omega$ and $N$-spot equilibria to confirm asymptotic results\nand also to demonstrate how domain geometry impacts thresholds and dominant\noscillation modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 2 Jul 2022 11:34:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
